{"tid":233144,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"九頭身教師「犯規」衣著　短裙短到網民熱議","createTime":"2017-05-07T10:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T10:39:13.000Z","uid":81228,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"79b02b79598d6a02e6695dd8afbebb99130091a2","tid":233144,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T10:30:23.000Z","msg":"韓國一名女教師在個人社交網站晒生活照，這位九頭身美女超犯規的短裙，短到引來網民熱議不休。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/05/20170504_PN-%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F05%2F20170504_PN-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2596%2587%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25B8%25AB16.jpg&h=66899e5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nwoooozzzzz IG相片<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/05/20170504_PN-%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F05%2F20170504_PN-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2596%2587%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25B8%25AB09.jpg&h=a8d298b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/05/20170504_PN-%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F05%2F20170504_PN-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2596%2587%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25B8%25AB05.jpg&h=ff7d8dfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日一位網名「woooozzzzz」個人社交網站晒相，這位樣貌甜美，身材火辣的美女迅即吸引網民的目光，網民人肉起底，發現這位美女是一名英文教師，其職業曝光即引來網民熱烈討論。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/05/20170504_PN-%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F05%2F20170504_PN-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2596%2587%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25B8%25AB03.jpg&h=3912847c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/05/20170504_PN-%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F05%2F20170504_PN-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2596%2587%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25B8%25AB14.jpg&h=24ac9926&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/05/20170504_PN-%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F05%2F20170504_PN-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2596%2587%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25B8%25AB02.jpg&h=f5b884e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/05/20170504_PN-%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F05%2F20170504_PN-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2596%2587%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25B8%25AB17.jpg&h=aa239ec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目前這位女教師的個人社交網站已有超過七萬名粉絲。網民的焦點都放在總以超辣短裙示人的這位索女，在上課教書時衣著有否犯規：「真的是老師嗎？」「常常穿窄裙上課，光用想就讓人噴鼻血。」「想回去讀書，沒選到英文課好後悔。」有網民更發揮FF天分，討論起這位教師著短裙上講台授課會否走光。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/05/20170504_PN-%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F05%2F20170504_PN-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2596%2587%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25B8%25AB15.jpg&h=e80699b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/05/20170504_PN-%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F05%2F20170504_PN-%25